---
/** In-game menu + controls + tutorial + abandon confirm — always inside #game-shell. */
---

<div class="game-menu" data-game-menu hidden>
  <div class="game-menu__card" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="game-menu-title">
    <h2 class="game-menu__title" id="game-menu-title">Menú</h2>
    <button type="button" class="btn" data-menu-resume>Reanudar</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-menu-controls>Controles</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-menu-sound>Sonido</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-menu-fullscreen hidden>Volver a pantalla completa</button>
    <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-menu-abandon>Abandonar partido</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="game-controls-help" data-controls-help hidden>
  <div class="game-controls-help__card" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="controls-help-title">
    <h3 id="controls-help-title">Controles</h3>

    <div class="controls-sheet" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="controls-sheet__keys">
        <span class="controls-key controls-key--up" data-bind-label="up">W</span>
        <span class="controls-key controls-key--left" data-bind-label="left">A</span>
        <span class="controls-key controls-key--down" data-bind-label="down">S</span>
        <span class="controls-key controls-key--right" data-bind-label="right">D</span>
        <p class="controls-sheet__caption">Mover</p>
      </div>
      <div class="controls-sheet__mouse">
        <div class="controls-mouse">
          <span class="controls-mouse__btn controls-mouse__btn--left"></span>
          <span class="controls-mouse__btn controls-mouse__btn--right"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="controls-mouse__legend">
          <span><span class="controls-mouse__dot controls-mouse__dot--left"></span> <b data-bind-label="pass">Clic izquierdo</b> · Pase</span>
          <span><span class="controls-mouse__dot controls-mouse__dot--right"></span> <b data-bind-label="tackle">Clic derecho</b> · Entrada</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="game-controls-help__lead">Toca un control para reasignarlo.</p>
    <ul class="game-controls-remap" data-controls-remap></ul>
    <p class="game-controls-remap__conflict" data-controls-conflict hidden>
      Hay controles repetidos. Reasigna los marcados en rojo.
    </p>

    <div class="game-controls-help__actions">
      <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-controls-reset>Restablecer</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn" data-controls-help-close>Cerrar</button>
    </div>
    <p class="game-controls-help__hint" data-controls-help-hint>En juego: controla tu jugador y busca el gol.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="game-tutorial" data-controls-tutorial hidden>
  <div class="game-tutorial__card" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="controls-tutorial-title">
    <h2 class="game-tutorial__title" id="controls-tutorial-title">Cómo se juega</h2>
    <p class="game-tutorial__lead">Estos son tus controles. Podrás cambiarlos cuando quieras desde el menú.</p>
    <ul class="game-tutorial__list" data-tutorial-list></ul>
    <div class="game-tutorial__actions">
      <button type="button" class="btn" data-tutorial-ok>Entendido</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-tutorial-configure>Configurar controles</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="game-confirm" data-abandon-confirm hidden>
  <div class="game-confirm__card" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
    <p>¿Abandonar el partido? Se contará como derrota / abandono.</p>
    <div class="game-confirm__actions">
      <button type="button" class="btn" data-abandon-confirm-yes>Abandonar</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn-outline" data-abandon-confirm-no>Cancelar</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
